name: YOLOw
tagline: Notification System for Laptop Battery Life
body:
Ever find yourself leaving your laptop unplugged only to find it DEAD when you come back?
What if you could save its life?
Now you can receive an **INSTANT** notification when your battery is low!
Introducing YOLOw!

Free software available for Windows/Mac and Linux Based Systems.
Download Here:
[Windows Installallation v. 0.3](https://linx.li/selif/9cnt64pix.exe)
```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```
